This is the README file for the binary distribution of GVD.
This directory contains the files needed for installing and running GVD.

INSTALLING

The quick way to install GVD is to run the script 'doinstall' contained
in this directory and then follow the instructions.

USE

Using GVD is documented in the GVD user's guide available in HTML format using
the F1 key under GVD itself, or as text and info files in the directory
$base/doc/gvd, where $base is the base directory chosen when installing GVD
(using doinstall).

